7-3-101, 87-3-103, 87-3-105, 87-3-107, 87-3-109, 87-3-111 And 87-3-113, Mississippi Code Of 1972, Which Provide The Uniform Durable Power Of Attorney Act; And For Related Purposes.</description><committee/><history><step><date>2014-01-20</date><action>Referred To Judiciary, Division A</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2014-02-04</date><action>Title Suff Do Pass Comm Sub</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-02-12</date><action>Committee Substitute Adopted</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-02-12</date><action>Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-02-12</date><action>Passed As Amended</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2014-02-14</date><action>Transmitted To House</action><chamber>S</chamber><chamber_id>58</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-02-17</date><action>Referred To Judiciary A</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>1</importance></step><step><date>2014-03-04</date><action>Title Suff Do Pass</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-03-11</date><action>Amended</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-03-11</date><action>Passed As Amended</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-03-11</date><action>Motion to Reconsider Entered (Malone, Baker, Reynolds)</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></step><step><date>2014-03-13</date><action>Motion to Reconsider Tabled</action><chamber>H</chamber><chamber_id>57</chamber_id><importance>0</importance></